<BaseLayout title="Refunds — Janaushdhi" description="Janaushdhi refund policy.">
  <div class="page prose">
    <span class="pill">Legal</span>
    <h1 style="margin-top:12px;">Refunds</h1>
    <p>Janaushdhi is a free public-health information site. We do not sell anything, do not accept payments, and therefore have no refund obligations.</p>
    <p>If you purchased a medicine at a Jan Aushadhi Kendra and need to return it, please contact the Kendra directly or follow guidance at <a href="https://www.janaushadhi.gov.in/" rel="noopener external">janaushadhi.gov.in</a>.</p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
